headline: US RevPAR will decline in 2025: CoStar, Tourism Economics
summary: In their final hotel forecast revision of the year, the companies further downgraded their full-year outlook, now expecting RevPAR to drop 0.4% amid rising costs and policy uncertainty.

headline: 2 Safe-and-Steady Stocks with Exciting Potential and 1 We Ignore
summary: Low-volatility stocks may offer stability, but that often comes at the cost of slower growth and the upside potential of more dynamic companies.
